  • 封闭类:

    public static class MyntManager.Parameters
extends java.lang.Object
    zh:

    扫描参数

    扫描发现设备时参数配置，调用MyntManager setParameters 设置 扫描参数。不设置，则会使用默认参数，默认是每隔5秒扫描一次，每次扫描持续2秒。扫描最小间隔2秒，发现设备超时时间15秒。 en: Scan parameters

    Scan found the device parameter configuration, call setParameters MyntManager settings Scan parameter. Do not set up, you will use the default parameters, the default is to scan every 5 seconds, each scan lasts 2 seconds. Scanning minimum interval of 2 seconds, 15 seconds to find the device time.
